flowchart LR
    user[Telegram user] --> bot[aiogram bot]
    bot --> download[Temporary image download]
    download --> ocr[OpenRouter multimodal OCR]
    ocr --> note[Obsidian Markdown note]
    ocr --> preview[Reduced JPEG preview]
    preview --> attachments[(Obsidian attachments)]
    attachments --> note
    note --> vault[(Obsidian Vault)]
    bot --> status[Text-only Telegram status]
